WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.506 --> 00:00:07.841 line:0%
 
TODAY, WE'RE GONNA
TALK ABOUT THE ALAMO

00:00:07.875 --> 00:00:10.944 line:0%
 
IN SAN ANTONIO, TEXAS.

00:00:12.179 --> 00:00:15.816 line:0%
 
1836--
ENTER WILLIAM TRAVIS.

00:00:15.849 --> 00:00:18.552 line:0%
 
DODGED OUT ON A BUNCH
OF BUSINESS DEBTS,

00:00:18.585 --> 00:00:21.154 line:0%
 
HE ABANDONED HIS WIFE
AND CHILD

00:00:21.188 --> 00:00:25.792 line:0%
 
AND HEADED TOWARDS TEXAS
WITH HIS SLAVE, JOE.

00:00:25.826 --> 00:00:29.196 line:0%
 
JIM BOWIE, HE FORGED
THESE DOCUMENTS THAT HE OWNED

00:00:29.229 --> 00:00:31.832 line:0%
 
ALL THESE GRANTS
IN THE UNITED STATES TERRITORY.

00:00:31.865 --> 00:00:34.501 line:0%
 
JIM BOWIE'S LIKE,
YEAH, THEY'RE ONTO ME HERE.

00:00:34.535 --> 00:00:35.702 line:0%
 
I BETTER GET TO TEXAS,

00:00:35.736 --> 00:00:37.471 line:0%
 
WHERE THEY'RE PROBABLY
NOT AS SMART,

00:00:37.504 --> 00:00:41.842 line:0%
 
AND I'LL START DOING THIS
SAME SHENANIGAN DOWN THERE.

00:00:41.875 --> 00:00:45.045 line:0%
 
CONGRESSMAN DAVY CROCKETT,

00:00:45.078 --> 00:00:46.713 line:0%
 
EVERYBODY LOVES THIS GUY.

00:00:46.747 --> 00:00:47.881 line:0%
 
THE SAYING GOES,

00:00:47.915 --> 00:00:50.717 line:0%
 
"HE COULD KILL A GRIZZLY BEAR
WITH HIS SMILE."

00:00:50.751 --> 00:00:52.452 line:0%
 
WELL, AS IT HAPPENS,

00:00:52.486 --> 00:00:54.421 line:0%
 
HE DOESN'T GET ELECTED
FOR A SECOND TERM.

00:00:54.454 --> 00:00:57.257
AND HE SAYS,
YOU CAN GO TO HELL.

00:00:57.291 --> 00:00:58.825
I'LL GO TO TEXAS.

00:00:58.859 --> 00:01:03.864
CROCKETT, TRAVIS, AND BOWIE
HEAD TO TEXAS TO TAKE LAND.

00:01:08.135 --> 00:01:11.438
MEXICO OWNS THE TERRITORY
OF TEXAS,

00:01:11.471 --> 00:01:13.841
AND THE LONG-STORY-SHORT
IS THESE GUYS

00:01:13.874 --> 00:01:16.977
EXPEL A MEXICAN ARMY
GARRISON

00:01:17.077 --> 00:01:20.280
AND THEY TAKE A MISSION
FOR THEMSELVES.

00:01:22.549 --> 00:01:26.620
AND THAT MISSION
IS THE ALAMO.

00:01:26.653 --> 00:01:29.089
AND THEY HOLE UP
IN THE ALAMO.

00:01:29.089 --> 00:01:30.791
BOWIE SAYS, DON'T WORRY.

00:01:30.824 --> 00:01:32.926
THERE'S NO WAY
THE MEXICAN ARMY'S

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:36.096
COMING UNTIL SPRING,
BECAUSE THE WINTER'S TOO HARSH

00:01:36.096 --> 00:01:39.800
ON THESE
HIGH MEXICAN DESERTS.

00:01:39.833 --> 00:01:41.535
BUT THEY DO COME.

00:01:41.568 --> 00:01:45.239
SANTA ANNA AND HIS SOLDIERS
ARRIVE IN SAN ANTONIO.

00:01:45.272 --> 00:01:46.640
THEY'RE ON HIS LAND.

00:01:46.673 --> 00:01:48.742
AND HE SAYS
TO THE ALAMO DEFENDERS,

00:01:48.775 --> 00:01:52.279
SURRENDER NOW
OR YOU WILL BE KILLED.

00:01:52.312 --> 00:01:53.814
[scoffs]

00:01:53.847 --> 00:01:54.982
BULL[bleep].

00:01:55.015 --> 00:01:57.584
LET'S FIRE A CANNON SHOT
AT SANTA ANNA

00:01:57.618 --> 00:01:59.286
AND LET HIM KNOW
WE KNOW BUSINESS.

00:01:59.319 --> 00:02:01.455
AND FIRES A CANNON.

00:02:01.488 --> 00:02:05.492
AND THIS PISSES OFF
SANTA ANNA.

